GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=commitsCount
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Get Top Topics (Pull Requests Count)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/topics/top?limit=5&sortBy=pullRequestsCount
